# Function Plotter

A simple web application built with Streamlit that plots a linear function

## Features
- Currently plot y = 2x + 3 (Will update so user can change slope and y-intercept)

## How to run locally
1. Clone the repository
`git clone https://github.com/tdnguyen04/graphing-streamlit-basics.git`
2. Create and activate virtual environment (optional)
`python -m venv venv`
`source venv/bin/activate` 
(!!! On Windows, use `venv\Scripts\activate`)
3. Install the required packages
`pip install -r requirements.txt`
4. Run the Streamlit app
`streamlit run app.py`

